
Package: TreeTwoWay
Type: Package
Title: Likelihood Ratio and MINMIN/MINMAX Tests for Two-Way ANOVA Under Tree Order Restriction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Susmita", "Chawlia",
                  email = "susmitachawlia16@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut","cre"))
Description:
  Provides three hypothesis testing procedures for two-way ANOVA
under tree-order restrictions:
  (1) Likelihood Ratio Test (TreeLRT),
(2) MINMIN test (TreeMinMn), and
(3) MINMAX test (TreeMinMax).
All functions use parametric bootstrap to obtain critical values
under heteroscedasticity and unequal sample sizes.
